<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>
@EM{{@HI{{dokoroka}}}} is a conjunction that indicates that something is very far from an expected state.
The situation in the clause following @EM{{@HI{{dokoroka}}}} is very different to that stated in the clause preceding it.
</p>

